message:
Saving question tag in answers log:
- Adding new "TAG" column;
- Repeating question sequence number when tagging is automatic;
- Writing cleaned (removing initial equal/white space characters, double quoting entire text) question tag when manually defined by the users;

. CameraMain.java: fix to not show development mode if it has not been toggled on - it was checking only the "show validation process" setting;
. DrawView.java: change to draw an "X" indicating ignored invalid duplicate in scan cycle;
. TopcodeValidator.java: adding duplicate check also when the answer has already been validated;
